            # 椰꾧퀡???좎럡?묈뜝? shortlist ??좎럩彛????좎럩??筌왖??筌띲끉??筌띲끇猷???좎?????좎럥??
            try:
                score += math.log10(max(trade_value, 1.0))
            except Exception:
                pass

